00:24:09,440 --> 00:24:10,640
It gets theoretical, yes.

393
00:24:10,840 --> 00:24:20,680
They embed the amplitwist operators into what they call relativistic scalar vector plenum fields, RSVP fields.

394
00:24:20,680 --> 00:24:21,080
Yes.

