00:25:07,460 --> 00:25:10,260
The actor's name is the peak of the salience field.

407
00:25:10,380 --> 00:25:10,700
Yes.

408
00:25:10,700 --> 00:25:14,640
It's the highest potential point on the landscape that my brain is trying to reach.

409
00:25:14,820 --> 00:25:15,300
Exactly.

410
00:25:16,220 --> 00:25:19,680
The second field is the vector field, represented by Valern.

411
00:25:20,160 --> 00:25:20,680
Yes.

412
00:25:21,320 --> 00:25:21,920
Velocity.

413
00:25:22,180 --> 00:25:27,320
It encodes the direction and the speed of your changing thought in the current moment.

414
00:25:27,560 --> 00:25:32,240
It is the actual movement of your representation through the space.

415
00:25:33,040 --> 00:25:34,960
So salience is where I want to go.

416
00:25:35,280 --> 00:25:39,260
Velocity is how fast and in what direction I am currently moving.

417
00:25:39,260 --> 00:25:40,040
You got it.

418
00:25:40,700 --> 00:25:45,420
And the third field is the entropy field, six olorols, which we just explored.

419
00:25:45,740 --> 00:25:46,600
The chaotic one.

420
00:25:46,820 --> 00:25:47,120
Right.

421
00:25:47,520 --> 00:25:55,700
This maps the biological admissibility of the path you are on, the danger, the uncertainty, the unpredictability of the terrain.

