00:26:13,540 --> 00:26:15,560
That's the semantical pulling at your thoughts.

430
00:26:15,700 --> 00:26:15,880
Yeah.

431
00:26:15,880 --> 00:26:23,860
Your physical raft and the direction and speed it is currently traveling over the water is the velocity, the dollars.

432
00:26:24,060 --> 00:26:24,380
Okay.

433
00:26:24,380 --> 00:26:30,480
And the entropy, the in your dollars, represents the physical turbulence of the river.

434
00:26:30,700 --> 00:26:31,000
Mm-hmm.

435
00:26:31,200 --> 00:26:36,680
The jagged rocks, the rapids, the chaotic, dangerous waters that could flip the raft.

