When you are writing an essay or writing code or playing an instrument and the next move just comes to you effortlessly, there's no friction.

451
00:27:39,720 --> 00:27:42,200
You are perfectly aligned with the salience gradient.

452
00:27:42,400 --> 00:27:45,780
But as you know, cognitive processes are rarely that smooth.

453
00:27:46,200 --> 00:27:47,220
Unfortunately, no.

454
00:27:47,220 --> 00:27:51,500
Often, your phase alignment is closer to 90 degrees.

455
00:27:52,780 --> 00:27:55,380
Your motion becomes orthogonal to the goal.

456
00:27:56,180 --> 00:27:57,240
You are moving sideways.

457
00:27:57,600 --> 00:27:58,120
Sideways.

458
00:27:58,240 --> 00:28:06,120
And the sideways movement in the field creates what the papal calls vorticity, represented by the Greek letter seksity.

