00:29:13,660 --> 00:29:14,420
On or off.

481
00:29:14,540 --> 00:29:14,800
Right.

482
00:29:15,180 --> 00:29:19,660
Yet our subjective experience of thought, like the river, feels continuous.

483
00:29:20,060 --> 00:29:20,360
True.

484
00:29:20,740 --> 00:29:25,020
To resolve this, Appendix D introduces the Trotter-Cato framework.

