00:29:35,100 --> 00:29:42,420
It provides a mathematical proof that discrete, step-by-step updates can converge into a continuous flow.

488
00:29:42,700 --> 00:29:43,280
Okay, how?

489
00:29:43,500 --> 00:29:49,700
Imagine your cognitive updates as individual discrete applications of the amplet-wist operator.

